window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Mikhail's power had only grown with every new day, and his Family was also flourishing. However, so were their enemies. New ones had emerged, and old ones who'd long ago written them off were now stirring.</p> <p>But really, was this a problem? He was a healer, and there was always a remedy, and mandatory \"treatment\" could not be stopped! Indeed, his enemies would pay handsomely for it. At least, whatever remained of them....</p>"; 
